wiki.content:
"Mannequin" is a 2008 song by Britney Spears off her 6th studio album, "Circus". A rehearsal video of the song lead to the anticipation of her VMA appearance in 2008, her album, and her 2009 tour in support of the album The Circus Starring Britney Spears.
